@startuml UC23_Sequence
title UC23: 同步课程信息 - 顺序图

actor "外部系统" as ExternalSystem
boundary "外部API连接器" as Connector
control "集成控制器" as IntegCtrl
entity "SyncRequest" as SyncReq
entity "Course" as Course

ExternalSystem -> Connector : 发送变更通知/数据包
Connector -> IntegCtrl : handleIncomingData(payload)
IntegCtrl -> SyncReq : recordRequest(payload)
IntegCtrl -> Course : findByExternalId(id)
IntegCtrl -> Course : updateOrInsert(data)
IntegCtrl --> Connector : HTTP 200 OK
Connector -> ExternalSystem : 同步完成
@enduml
